# spt runtime perch state (not source) — depth-safe (** ), so it's ignored under any nested
# .claude/ too (e.g. plugin/sptc/.claude/ when this repo is loaded as a live plugin). A
# root-anchored pattern previously leaked plugin/sptc/.claude/LIVE_AGENT_IDS.json into the tree.
**/.claude/LIVE_AGENT_IDS.json
**/.claude/*-commune.md
**/.claude/*-signoff.md

# generated launchers (capsule-style cc / cc-<id>)
/cc
/cc.bat
/cc.sh
/cc-*
